A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending The Sunshine House on its 50th anniversary; and for other
2 purposes.
3 WHEREAS, The Sunshine House has provided high-quality early childhood education and
4 care for 50 years, positively impacting the lives of more than 300,000 children since its
5 founding in 1975; and
6 WHEREAS, The Sunshine House was founded by Dennis and Roseann Drew, who, as new
7 parents in 1974, sought to create an early learning environment that met the highest standards
8 of care and education for their daughter, leading to the establishment of Small World
9 Preschool, which later became The Sunshine House; and
10 WHEREAS, what began as a single in-home preschool has grown into one of the largest
11 early education and childcare providers in the nation, now operating 119 schools across six
12 states with seven more planned for the future; and
13 WHEREAS, The Sunshine House nurtures and educates more than 12,000 children daily
14 through the dedication of over 1,800 educators who provide a safe, engaging, and enriching
15 environment for early learning; and
