16 WHEREAS, the organization's commitment to growth and innovation has included
17 significant milestones such as its expansion into North Carolina in 1995 and Georgia in the
18 late 1990s, the launch of The Quest Zone Afterschool Program in 2000, and the
19 establishment of the first Foundations Early Learning Center in 2016; and
20 WHEREAS, for half a century, The Sunshine House has upheld its mission of providing
21 high-quality care and education to every child and family it serves, fostering a legacy of
22 learning, development, and opportunity; and
23 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper to honor The Sunshine House for its 50 years
24 of dedication to early childhood education and its lasting contributions to children, families,
25 and communities in this state and beyond.
26 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
27 the members of this body recognize and commend The Sunshine House upon the grand
28 occasion of its 50th anniversary and extend best wishes for continued success.
29 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
30 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to The
31 Sunshine House.
